reviewText:
One of the very best Mexican comedies of all time. Juan Camaney is legendary doing dirty, flirty comedy.
The movie is great but this is an edited version. It cuts out all the very good parts, most of these scenes are the funnier dirty scenes.
I am not happy with all the content that is missing but the movie is still good.

Beware that is is the edited version.
its not the original version which takes away from the laughter i ordered it thinking after all this time of searchin i would have it. i got it all right junk.
